# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# iOS Software Factory – Environment Variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your keys.

# ── GitHub Models (works with GitHub Copilot subscription) ──
# 1. Go to https://github.com/settings/tokens
# 2. Generate a new token (classic) – no special scopes needed
# 3. Paste the token below
GITHUB_TOKEN=github_pat_...

# Model to use from GitHub Models (pick one):
# gpt-4o  |  gpt-4o-mini  |  Meta-Llama-3.1-405B-Instruct  |  mistral-large
GITHUB_MODEL=gpt-4o

# ── Fallback: direct OpenAI key (if you have one) ──
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
